Layihə 2 – Top Employee by Department
Məqsəd

Hər departamentdə ən yüksək maaş alan işçini tapmaq.

İstifadə olunan SQL mövzuları
WITH (CTE)
ROW_NUMBER()
PARTITION BY
JOIN
WITH a AS (
    SELECT first_name,
           last_name,
           department_id,
           salary,
           ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
               PARTITION BY department_id
               ORDER BY salary DESC
           ) AS rn
    FROM employees
)
SELECT r.first_name,
       r.last_name,
       d.department_name,
       r.salary
FROM a r
JOIN departments d
ON r.department_id = d.department_id
WHERE rn = 1
ORDER BY d.department_name;
